name: Kelsch Associates
specialty: Community Based Residential Treatment Facility  Intellectual and/or Developmental Disabilities

narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Kelsch Associates is a Community Based Residential Treatment Facility  Intellectual and/or Developmental Disabilities provider based in Woodbury Heights, NJ. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $117.4M in Medicaid payments across 97K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: This provider received $117.4M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 14,678 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
